The paper deals with wireless communication systems and optimization of their performance, which falls under the scope of information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The use of intelligent reflecting surfaces (IRS) also involves control and systems engineering (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of multiple antennas and elements, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and computer communications (cs.COM).
